PerlIO-nline version 0.02
=========================

This module provides an alternative to the standard :crlf layer.
This layer translates any of \r, \n or \r\n into \n on input, and
to \r\n on output.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

perl 5.8.0, XSLoader

